Classes in org.objectstyle.cayenne.access used by org.objectstyle.cayenne
DataContext
          Class that provides applications with access to Cayenne persistence features.
 

Classes in org.objectstyle.cayenne.access used by org.objectstyle.cayenne.access
DataContext
          Class that provides applications with access to Cayenne persistence features.
DataContextDelegate
          Defines API for a DataContext "delegate" - an object that is temporarily passed control by DataContext at some critical points in the normal flow of execution.
DataDomain
          DataDomain performs query routing functions in Cayenne.
DataNode
          Describes a single physical data source.
DataRowStore
          A fixed size cache of DataRows keyed by ObjectId.
DbLoaderDelegate
          DbLoaderDelegate defines API that allows to control the behavior of DbLoader during the database reverse-engineering.
IncrementalFaultList
          A synchronized list that serves as a container of DataObjects.
ObjectStore
          ObjectStore maintains a cache of objects and their snapshots.
OperationHints
          Defines an API that allows QueryEngine to obtain information about query execution.
OperationObserver
          Defines a set of callback methods for a QueryEngine to notify interested object about different stages of queries execution.
QueryEngine
          Defines methods used to run Cayenne queries.
ResultIterator
          Defines API of an iterator over the records returned as a result of SelectQuery execution.
Transaction
          Class responsible for transaction management within Cayenne.
TransactionDelegate
          Defines callback methods for customizing Cayenne transaction behavior.
